      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GINNY'S RUN (1) was the fastest winner on the program last time out, running away to score by 8 lengths (37.53) at Gawler. Can measure up again. BEDROCK CAM (7) was well in the market last time but only managed fourth (44.44), beaten 16 lengths. Finished second the start before. Expected to give a good account. FANTASTIC HELGA (5) goes very well at the distance with five wins and a placing from 12 starts. Missed the frame latest (31.03) when seventh over 530m at Murray Bridge in a Grade 4/5. Looks well placed here and among the chances. WEBLEC POLLY (3) was well fancied last time on the strength of her recent form but could only manage second (43.73) at this track. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Likely to be in the finish again.",
